places.title: From Recife: Tour Olinda with Recife Antigo

attributes.label: Must book at least 10h in advance

places.abstract: Take a guided day trip from Boa Viagem or Piedade to explore UNESCO-listed Olinda's historic churches and landmarks, Recife Antigo's vibrant streets, and the Handicraft Center of Pernambuco.

places.title: Recife: City Tour Recife & Olinda

attributes.label: Must book at least 10h in advance

places.abstract: Immerse yourself in the enchanting beauty of Olinda, one of the most breathtaking colonial cities that exudes a magical charm. We'll also venture into the vibrant Recife Antigo neighborhood.

places.title: Recife: Brazil eSIM Roaming Mobile Data Plan
places.abstract: Scan a QR code for instant access to the local high-speed data network with your eSIM- compatible device no matter where you are and when it is. Benefit from reasonable pricing, a reliable network, and support.

places.title: Olinda City Tour and Instituto Ricardo Brennand

attributes.label: Must book at least 24h in advance

places.abstract: Explore one of the best-preserved colonial cities in Brazil on a 5-hour guided tour of Olinda from Recife. See landmark attractions with a guide, including the panoramic lift of the Caixa da Agua no Alto da Sé, the Ricardo Brennard Museum and more.

places.title: Recife Boat Tour with Transfers

attributes.label: Must book at least 4h in advance

places.abstract: Cruise along the Capibaribe River in Recife and experience the "Brazilian Venice" by water. Ride to Santo Antonio, Recife Antigo and Boa Vista islands passing bridges and colonial buildings. Discover where the Portuguese founded the city.

questionsAndAnswers.question:
(Translated by Google) Is there a ticket to visit the Sissi museum only? How much does it cost? Thank you

(Original)
Esiste un biglietto per visitare solo il museo di Sissi? Quanto costa? Grazie
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
(Translated by Google) The ticket is unique and with this you visit the silverware museum, the Sissi museum and the royal apartments. The cost is 13.90 euros for adults and 8.20 euros for children, it is possible to make a family ticket. I recommend going in, it's worth it.

(Original)
Il biglietto è unico e con questo si visita il museo delle argenterie, il museo di Sissi e gli appartamenti reali. Il costo è di 13.90 euro per gli adulti e 8.20 euro i bimbi, possibile fare biglietto famiglia. Consiglio di entrare, vale la pena.

places.title: Private Algiers Airport transfers to/from Annaba city

attributes.label: Must book at least 24h in advance

places.abstract: Book a private 1-way private transfer from Algiers International Airport to your accommodation in Annaba province or visa versa. Choose which size of vehicle you want, then hop in and enjoy the ride.

places.title: Annaba: Algeria eSIM Roaming Mobile Data Plan
places.abstract: Scan a QR code for instant access to the local high-speed data network with your eSIM- compatible device no matter where you are and when it is. Benefit from reasonable pricing, a reliable network, and support.

places.title: *6 Hr All The Attractions Cruise Terminal Pickup & Drop Off

attributes.label: Must book at least 30min in advance

places.abstract: Experience Acapulco at its best on a guided shore excursion tour. Get to know Acapulco better and deeper as you explore a local market, see the Chapel of Peace, and visit La Quebrada.

places.title: *4-Hour Roqueta Island Snorkeling and/or Paddle Boarding

attributes.label: Must book at least 30min in advance

places.abstract: Enjoy a beach break at Caleta beach and experience one hour of Paddle Boarding and/or snorkeling at the Island of La Roqueta with your own instructor before savoring a delicious Mexican lunch.

places.title: *4 Hours Shore Excursion With Cruise Ship Terminal Pick Up.

attributes.label: Must book at least 30min in advance

places.abstract: If you are visiting Acapulco on a cruise this tour is for you. Admire the famous divers of La Quebrada, see old and new Acapulco, the Chapel of Peace, and many more sights on this shore excursion.

places.title: Acapulco: Acarey Catamaran Cruise with Party
places.abstract: Enjoy Acapulco Bay in the best way, choose between an afternoon or night tour. Take part in a party on board, dance to live music, and have some drinks, all while enjoying spectacular views.

places.title: .Acapulco History Cultural Tour & Cliff Divers Show w/Lunch

attributes.label: Must book at least 45min in advance

places.abstract: Take a guided tour of historical Acapulco. You'll see the fortress showcasing the area's complete history, the Diego Rivera mural and visit the cathedral, amongst others. Finish the tour by watching the spectacular Cliff Divers Show and have lunch.

places.title: .Baby Turtle Release, Lagoon Boat Ride, and Crocodile Farm

attributes.label: Must book at least 30min in advance

places.abstract: This tour is a must for nature lovers. Drive along the coast admiring mango and coconut plantations, learn about the lifestyle of the locals and visit a crocodile farma. Upon arriving at Tres Palos Lagoon, you'll board a private motorboat.
